33:51.646 --> 33:55.511
public loves astronomy. I think the public 
doesn't think there's any difference between

33:55.591 --> 34:02.661
planetary astronomy and stellar astronomy. They 
look at it all as being the study of the universe,

34:03.743 --> 34:09.530
which I think is the way it should be looked at.

