Mars first and raising the American flag. And all 
of this has helped us to develop

36:43.417 --> 36:54.294
or I developed the funding for astronomy as part of 
this other great job that we have to do for the

36:43.417 --> 36:54.294
country. And that's all changed.

37:03.569 --> 37:07.315
What do you think was the effect, if any, I guess 
maybe I should just, I left that sort of quickly.

